<ab facs="#facs_612_r1l7"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heım</expan> </ab>
